<module>
    <h>fuirich</h>
    <p><g>fuirich</g>
        <en>wait, stay, live</en> is a <a href="?xx=verbs/simple_verbs">simple verb</a>.</p>

    <section id="forms">
        <h>forms</h>
        <p>The principal parts of <g>fuirich</g> are – <ul>
            <li><m>fuirichidh</m> – future independent – <en>will stay</en></li>
            <li><m>dh’fhuirich</m> – past independent – <en>stayed</en></li>
            <li><m>fuireachd</m>
                <fem/> – verbal noun – <en>staying</en></li>
        </ul>
        </p>
        <section id="forms-tense">
            <h>tense</h>
            <p><ul>
                <li>past <ul id="past">
                    <li>active <ul>
                        <li>independent – <m>dh’fhuirich</m></li>
                        <li>relative – a <m>dh’fhuirich</m></li>
                        <li>dependent – cha/an/nach <m>do dh’fhuirich</m></li>
                    </ul>
                    </li>
                    <li>passive <ul>
                        <li>independent – <m>dh’fhuiricheadh</m></li>
                        <li>relative – a <m>dh’fhuiricheadh</m></li>
                        <li>dependent – cha/an/nach <m>do dh’fhuiricheadh</m></li>
                    </ul>
                    </li>
                </ul>
                </li>
                <li>future <ul id="future">
                    <li>active <ul>
                        <li>independent – <m>fuirichidh</m></li>
                        <li>relative – a <m>dh’fuiricheas</m></li>
                        <li>dependent – chan/nach <m>fhuirich</m>, am <m>fuirich</m></li>
                    </ul>
                    </li>
                    <li>passive <ul>
                        <li>independent – <m>fuirichear</m></li>
                        <li>relative – a <m>dh’fhuirichear</m></li>
                        <li>dependent – chan/nach <m>fhuirichear</m>, am <m>fuirichear</m></li>
                    </ul>
                    </li>
                </ul>
                </li>
                <li>conditional <ul id="conditional">
                    <li>active <ul>
                        <li>first person singular <ul>
                            <li>independent – <m>dh’fhuirichinn</m></li>
                            <li>relative – a <m>dh’fhuirichinn</m></li>
                            <li>dependent – chan/nach <m>fhuirichinn</m>, am <m>fuirichinn</m></li>
                        </ul>
                        </li>
                        <li>first person plural <ul>
                            <li>independent – <m>dh’fhuiricheamaid</m></li>
                            <li>relative – a <m>dh’fhuiricheamaid</m></li>
                            <li>dependent – chan/nach <m>fhuiricheamaid</m>, am <m>fuiricheamaid</m></li>
                        </ul>
                        </li>
                        <li>second/third persons <ul>
                            <li>independent – <m>dh’fhuiricheadh</m></li>
                            <li>relative – a <m>dh’fhuiricheadh</m></li>
                            <li>dependent – chan/nach <m>fhuiricheadh</m>, am <m>fuiricheadh</m></li>
                        </ul>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                    </li>
                    <li>passive <ul>
                        <li>independent – <m>dh’fhuirichte</m></li>
                        <li>relative – a <m>dh’fhuirichte</m></li>
                        <li>dependent – chan/nach <m>fhuirichte</m>, am <m>fuirichte</m></li>
                    </ul>
                    </li>
                </ul>
                </li>
            </ul></p>
